The **solution behavior** required (from vulnerability knowledge) is:

> "Ensure that the length of the user-provided buffer is consistently validated against the actual sizes of the data structures involved. This includes correctly setting the address length field based on the socket type and making sure that any copying of data into user space considers the proper size limits."

